--------------------------------------------------------------------------
def: ^controlStrategy
is: ^marker
doc: "Control logic or strategy that is programmed into a system or equip"
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
def: ^controlStrategyType
is: ^marker
doc: "Control logic or strategy that is programmed into a system or equip"
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
def: ^singleStage
is: ^choice
of: ^controlStrategyType
doc: "Control is implemented via single boolean cmd point."
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
def: ^multiStage
is: ^choice
of: ^controlStrategyType
doc:
  Control is implemented via multiple boolean cmd points.  Each
  point should be modeled separately.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
def: ^continuous
is: ^choice
of: ^controlStrategyType
doc:
  Control is implemented via a single numeric cmd point, typically
  0% - 100%.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------